@startuml
title Class Group Enrollment - State Diagram
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAF7
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #9A8700

[*] --> trial : trial enrollment
[*] --> active : regular enrollment with capacity
[*] --> waitlisted : no available capacity

trial --> active : confirms enrollment / capacity available
trial --> withdrawn : leaves during trial / reason
trial --> completed : trial period completed
waitlisted --> active : seat becomes available
waitlisted --> withdrawn : cancels request / reason
active --> frozen : temporary pause
frozen --> active : resumes within episode
active --> withdrawn : early exit / reason required
frozen --> withdrawn : definitive exit / reason required
active --> completed : academic period completed
frozen --> completed : period closed by director

withdrawn --> [*]
completed --> [*]

note right of active
Counts against group capacity and
covers sessions between startsAt/endsAt.
end note

note bottom of withdrawn
Terminal state. History is preserved.
end note

note bottom of completed
Terminal state indicating the student
finished the class/program period.
end note

note left of trial
Hard delete is allowed only for an erroneous
enrollment with no attendance history.
end note
@enduml

